<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<style>
  body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #222; line-height: 1.65; max-width: 580px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
  .footer { margin-top: 28px; padding-top: 14px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; font-size: 12px; color: #777; }
  .sig { margin-top: 20px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<p>Hi {% if first_name %}{{ first_name }}{% else %}there{% endif %},</p>

<p>My name is {{ sender_name }} — I run {{ business_name }}, a small construction crew based in Bethesda that does unit turns, punch-list work, and ongoing maintenance for rental properties in {% if county == "montgomery" %}Montgomery County{% elif county == "prince_georges" %}Prince George's County{% else %}Montgomery and Prince George's Counties{% endif %}.</p>

{% if personalization_line %}
<p>{{ personalization_line }}</p>
{% endif %}

<p>We handle the work that comes up repeatedly between tenants and during renovations: painting, drywall, flooring, fixture and hardware replacement, and general cosmetic repairs. We're insured, and our W-9 is on file and ready for vendor onboarding.</p>

<p>Would you be willing to pass this along to whoever handles vendor approvals or maintenance scheduling? Or if that's you, I'd love to connect about any upcoming turns or repairs — even just getting on your approved-vendor list would be great.</p>

<div class="sig">
<p>Thanks,<br>
<strong>{{ sender_name }}</strong><br>
{{ business_name }}<br>
{{ business_phone }}<br>
{{ business_email }}</p>
</div>

<div class="footer">
  {{ business_name }} &middot; {{ physical_mailing_address }}<br>
  <small>
    This is a one-time business introduction. To opt out permanently,
    <a href="{{ unsubscribe_url }}">click here</a> or reply with "unsubscribe" and you won't hear from us again.
  </small>
</div>

</body>
</html>
